/>\n<br />\n營商的丈夫無論家庭背景及經濟能力下均遠勝Lily，結果雙方協議下，女兒撫養權歸丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n為免女兒失去母愛，Lily堅持每天下班後探望愛女，還在屯門夫家住所附近，以五千元租住劏房。<br />\n<br />\n她的一生，總是圍繞著不幸與傷悲 <br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180510/large/1525950275_0f09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180510%2Flarge%2F1525950275_0f09.jpg&h=1a0897cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180510/large/1525949669_8614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180510%2Flarge%2F1525949669_8614.jpg&h=42b50927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180514/2_586627_0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F2_586627_0%2F&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=05183981\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F2_586627_0%2F&h=bad495b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180514/2_586627_0/</a><br />\n<br />\n樣好似唔差有冇人埋單?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"又一個俾人奶害死既媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5da40738c1e0787f068c15884e870cb59245c7","tid":665031,"uid":124107,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f07b6eab6c25c87703b13085cb8ce78a6804b3c","tid":665031,"uid":2638,"like":17,"dislike":11,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"其實真心唔建議喂人奶<br />\n聽埋d 俾最好既bb<br />\n會迫死個媽咪<br />\n真心好辛苦"},{"pid":"14bb35ed55207f6a2c5e7f16bc0a2a7b7a94d1f2","tid":665031,"uid":38904,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"55435990c05c3c30a9ecd050d1c776042749c6fe","tid":665031,"uid":2638,"like":1,"dislike":17,"